OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 13 JUN
OL,4,CEVENTS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1965FGavin Gray, senior duty news
OL,7,Feditor, stepped in to read the 6.10pm
OL,8,Fnews (BBC One), due to a clerical error
OL,9,Fon the newsreaders' rota. The broadcast
OL,10,Fshould've been anchored by Richard
OL,11,FBaker.
OL,12,
OL,13,FGray's sartorial choice was widely
OL,14,Freported in the national press the
OL,15,Ffollowing day, as he wore a sports
OL,16,Fjacket and a pullover instead of the
OL,17,Fusual attire for a BBC One news
OL,18,Fbulletin (a suit). A photo appeared in
OL,19,Fthe Daily Mail.
OL,20,
OL,21,
