OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 13 JUN
OL,4,CEVENTS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1989FMoira Stuart presents the Six
OL,7,Fo'Clock News (BBC One) for the first
OL,8,Ftime.
OL,9,
OL,10,CG1997FRichard McCourt and Kirsten
OL,11,FO'Brien, along with Otis the Aardvark,
OL,12,Fpresent the final CBBC continuity links
OL,13,F(BBC One) from Studio A (BBC Television
OL,14,FCentre, London).
OL,15,
OL,16,CG2003FBruce Forsyth guest-presents
OL,17,FHave I Got News for You?. The programme
OL,18,Ffeatures the memorable one-off segment
OL,19,FPlay Your Iraqi Cards Right.
